items.displayName: Exadata Database Cloud Service - Database Server - X8M
items.description: Each Database Server includes 1,390 GB of memory and supports enabling up to 50 OCPUs per Database Server.     Best practice is to enable a minimum of 2 OCPU per Database Server and scale up/down from that point as appropriate in increments of 2 per Database Server.   For example, if your service includes a total of 4 Database Servers, provision a minimum of 8 OCPUs then scale OCPUs up or down in multiples of 8 (2 OCPUs x 4 Database Servers).
